subject: resource/The_Elective_Affinities
object: The Elective Affinities (Italian: Le affinità elettive, French: Les affinités électives) is a 1996 Italian-French comedy film directed by Paolo and Vittorio Taviani. It was screened out of competition at the 1996 Cannes Film Festival.
